Alright, so we're going to start off
talking about what infrastructure

00:16:45.570 --> 00:16:48.810
you guys have to work with us.

00:16:48.830 --> 00:16:52.520
First of all, let's start off with
our Darwin repository.

00:16:52.540 --> 00:16:55.820
Our repository,
where most of our projects live,

00:16:55.820 --> 00:16:57.460
is beyond our firewall.

00:16:57.480 --> 00:17:00.320
So,
you guys can get at it fairly quickly.

00:17:00.490 --> 00:17:04.140
And our external Darwin developers
have direct access to it,

00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:04.640
too.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:09.010
We also have an internal repository
where some of our non-live projects

00:17:09.210 --> 00:17:11.450
live for a few specific reasons.

00:17:11.460 --> 00:17:15.710
Either we've got source code from
third parties that we can't release,

00:17:15.710 --> 00:17:19.950
there's some information we've received
