But we try to minimize that where
we can and keep our projects

00:17:24.220 --> 00:17:27.290
in the external repository
where you guys can get at them,

00:17:27.290 --> 00:17:32.710
read the history, read the comments,
know why we did things the way we did.

00:17:32.870 --> 00:17:35.810
