00:17:46.670 --> 00:17:50.260
And of course our Darwin developers
work with us and you,

00:17:50.260 --> 00:17:53.880
the community,
to incorporate changes and fixes

00:17:53.880 --> 00:17:56.350
into our code to make it better.

